  dialogueText: {fileID: 683197447}
  defaultDialogue:
  - Hello there! Would you mind helping me?
  - I need you to find all the misprinted bills.
  - "When we printed them, we didn\u2019t pay close attention."
  - The bills are on the tables to my right.
  - "In the leftmost office, on the table, there\u2019s a paper showing images of
    the correct and misprinted bills."
  - "Good luck \u2014 and don\u2019t forget to find every single one of them!"
  inactiveDialogue:
  - I am busy right now...
  relatedQuestName: Find first bank desk
  allowedQuestName: Talk to Nairobi
